query.value:
@CONCAT('<fetch version="1.0" output-format="xml-platform" mapping="logical" distinct="false">
    <entity name="account">
       <all-attributes />
       <filter type="and">
           <condition attribute="modifiedon" operator="on-or-after" value="'
           ,variables('V_LastMod')
           , '"/>
       </filter>
     </entity>
</fetch>')
